FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:5000

# Library Management API

API mau cho ung dung quan ly thu vien.

# Group Books

## Books Collection [/books]

### List Books [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
          {
            "id": 1,
            "title": "Clean Code",
            "author": "Robert C. Martin",
            "available": true
          }
        ]

### Create Book [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "title": "Domain-Driven Design",
          "author": "Eric Evans"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 2,
          "title": "Domain-Driven Design",
          "author": "Eric Evans",
          "available": true
        }

## Book Detail [/books/{bookId}]

+ Parameters
    + bookId: 1 (number, required) - ID cua sach

### Get Book [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1,
          "title": "Clean Code",
          "author": "Robert C. Martin",
          "available": true
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Book not found"
        }

# Group Members

## Members Collection [/members]

### List Members [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
          {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "Nguyen Van A",
            "email": "a@example.com"
          }
        ]

### Create Member [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "name": "Tran Thi B",
          "email": "b@example.com"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 2,
          "name": "Tran Thi B",
          "email": "b@example.com"
        }

# Group Loans

## Loans Collection [/loans]

### Create Loan [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "bookId": 1,
          "memberId": 2
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1,
          "bookId": 1,
          "memberId": 2,
          "status": "borrowed"
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Book is not available"
        }

## Return Loan [/loans/{loanId}/return]

+ Parameters
    + loanId: 1 (number, required) - ID cua phieu muon

### Return Book [PATCH]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1,
          "bookId": 1,
          "memberId": 2,
          "status": "returned"
        }

+ Response 404 (application/json)

        {
          "message": "Loan not found"
        }
